Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.86,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,710)\fs45}完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我說  我們這次文化祭是要演白雪公主對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優想要扮演什麼角色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你乘亂在吃什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.14,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,500)}「魔女與蘋果與姐姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.14,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,500)}「魔女與蘋果與姐姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊是一年級的教室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說…說的也是呢  我有點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優說她要演魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女是王妃吧  我也想演那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼魔女會那麼有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這邊為什麼飛出火花了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  優就是喜歡幹些稀奇古怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡奇怪了  明明很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小雫竟然會想要演魔女  真意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為仔細想了想王妃的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現有和自己重疊的部分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和鏡子裡的自己說話很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們先試一下鏡  然後決定誰來演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那位漂亮的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要來個蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要我要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那位漂亮的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好入戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  真可愛  真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個能叫可愛麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  哪個魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪邊都很微妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺到了視線…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  楓  美月會長在看這邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是又來監視春香和優了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是想演白雪公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是被發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先暫時撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好歹也是學生會長  怎麼能在走廊裡奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:13:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才只是腳步跨的比較大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  我只是路過而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾你們了吧  再見  優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是知道的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長你是對白雪公主有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但又說不出口所以才在這兒轉悠的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  我真的只是路過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別再解釋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看春香同學太入迷  一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近一直看到美月會長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,午休的時候經常像剛才那樣蹲在門後面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人竟然會幹那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別看她那樣  或許也鼓不起勇氣來搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:15:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  為什麼琴音這種時候不上去搭話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定是太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼小雫會覺得難過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長也要來出演白雪公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的  騙人的  我才不演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  這是我和你最後一次一起參加文化祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你了  就當是為了小優
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長  你意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:16:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起偷窺  參演才能不讓人起疑地對那倆人進行監視喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  參演的話就能有更多和春香同學說話的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我這個笨蛋  為了監視  我也加入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  美月會長說她來演白雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有說來演  但是我沒說要演白雪公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那有其它想要演的角色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真專一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先看一下劇本再決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來白雪公主是個什麼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:57.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,100)}簡單易懂的！白雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人  最後竟然有接吻鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  也沒說春香同學會演白雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學演王子的話也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學你演哪個角色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然小優演魔女的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就兼任王妃的侍從  王子和獵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想演獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你更應該演其它角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
